| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5155 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2a6da244-3dbe-5b7f-89b9-e9e57959afcf"
